<main role="main">
<article>
<h2>Interests</h2>
<ul>
<li>Quantum information: Foundation of quantum mechanics by information processing, nonlocality, generalized probabilistic theories, quantum computation.</li>
<li>Information theory: Low-density parity-check codes, belief propagation, graph covers, polar codes.</li>
<li>Computer science: Constraint satisfaction problems, fully polynomial-time approximation scheme for &#35;P-complete problems, holographic transformation, quantum computation.</li>
<li>Statistical physics: The Bethe approximation, cluster expansions, partition function zeros, replica method.</li>
</ul>
</article>
